{"tid":402182,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"到底世界上係咪真係有咁好既人？","createTime":"2017-09-16T08:38:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-17T09:40:32.000Z","uid":143686,"like":0,"dislike":39,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"c981278a3b4c7c77fb7f9d0b2c3d9bff2d2df269","tid":402182,"uid":143686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T08:38:23.000Z","msg":"琴日識左個人 幾好人 即係講野呀個人都幾nice 又好主動 唔係怕怕醜醜 <br />\n<br />\n然後佢好快睇穿左我一個缺點 但佢係指出後就叫我改善下 叫我一步一步咁去改改左佢 而唔係厭棄直接話：嘩乜你咁架 <br />\n<br />\n即係佢比我既印象係 呢個人唔錯 可深交 但岩岩諗深一層 真係有咁好既人？ 定係因為岩岩識 佢先至咁好態度 <br />\n<br />\nPS: 佢幾傾得 正正常常 樣唔差  如果佢性格真係咁好 咁佢係咪真係完美<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da24166430e4e68ff334479c3a6c2692c5f7ce58","tid":402182,"uid":34047,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T08:40:07.000Z","msg":"響邊識 咩野年紀層"},{"pid":"dc10c24299a1e9f10959f7a68d7e962bd163d2cb","tid":402182,"uid":139828,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T08:40:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"469c27ff2fc8fcce14508c6fcca9532256b90037","tid":402182,"uid":143686,"like":1,"dislike":62,"score":-61,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T08:42:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>響邊識 咩野年紀層</blockquote><br />\n夜場。。 二十到 純粹覺得呢個人好似唔係現實生活中出現咁 因為好到有啲假 又或者我見識少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83c6a00d707367509a944def4881224795ffc678","tid":402182,"uid":22359,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T08:42:56.000Z","msg":"可能扮出黎   通常表面咁好嘅人  都有啲隱藏性格 特殊癖好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad96919557790b513f78a4394601b3d5f5677e5d","tid":402182,"uid":143686,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T08:43:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果個樣係毒撚, 應該無人開post, 應該係靚仔</blockquote><br />\nUm 我都無講男定女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但唔係重點 只係 大家信唔信有啲咁既人 直到岩岩果刻佢都whatsapp提我記得改改佢"},{"pid":"edb4b48f2ea79f5adcda7eaa0a9a79548f5c9c2e","tid"