e":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T09:01:28.000Z","msg":"其實唔出奇，個世界咩人都有，只係呢類人比較少<br />\n不過提提你識得唔耐就唔好咁快爆哂自己啲嘢出嚟，防人之心不可無"},{"pid":"9c53ca3eb823198f3ae8f643ffadce9e40c1daa3","tid":402182,"uid":143686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T09:03:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實唔出奇，個世界咩人都有，只係呢類人比較少<br />\n不過提提你識得唔耐就唔好咁快爆哂自己啲嘢出嚟，防人之心不可無</blockquote><br />\n咁呢方面我都好小心 通常唔會同人講咁多自己野 除非好好朋友 如果唔係我多數都係講下戇鳩野搞笑野 心底既野唔會搬出黎同啲唔熟既人講 <br />\n希望佢係真心好人"},{"pid":"8b7c73f0d3edf9fd97c5244f412b52cdc9bdbd75","tid":402182,"uid":16055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T09:04:49.000Z","msg":"不過夜場講咩都無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bd66af3dee2345981a264a796e41d83944ffc4a","tid":402182,"uid":10208,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T09:05:17.000Z","msg":"........有咩咁好<br />\n呢啲係正常既人應該要做到既基本條件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4acfc63c4c9817b5c16f0d90e20adc91b6617c6b","tid":402182,"uid":59746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T09:05:51.000Z","msg":"你問個都係想證明你既諗法係岩"},{"pid":"a8f84cc66bbd8dc1b9296585416828651839fadf","tid":402182,"uid":146431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T09:06:01.000Z","msg":"處女座？"},{"pid":"c24e1e5fdb7ff381f53e3fd47ffc984bb32b358a","tid":402182,"uid":143686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T09:06:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>........有咩咁好<br />\n呢啲係正常既人應該要做到既基本條件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n即係 當我發現一個人既缺點 岩岩識 我唔會直接指出黎  佢個人夠直 同埋好既係佢鼓勵我慢慢改善戎左佢"},{"pid":"c0d06ff14f2d4abed59e27910744fb4432e43cc3","tid":402182,"uid":117664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T09:07:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>........有咩咁好<br />\n呢啲係正常既人應該要做到既基本條件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\